# Non-Markdown File Handling — superseded by IngestSubagent

- **Default handler**: Non-.md handling (companion .md, subtype, embed, backup, attempt move to 5-Attachments/[subtype], #needs-manual-move on failure) is executed by the **IngestSubagent** ([agents/ingest.mdc](.cursor/rules/agents/ingest.mdc)) as part of the Ingest/ flow.
- **Rollback**: Restore full content from version control or backup to revert to this rule as handler.
- **Reference**: [agents/ingest.mdc](.cursor/rules/agents/ingest.mdc), [Attachment-Subtype-Mapping](3-Resources/Attachment-Subtype-Mapping.md).
